{
  "stem": "25027.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the central part of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before the Russians came in, that day before, there was looting because the Poles were leaving to the Romanian border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could actually see Polish army units-- we were about 40-- 30 or 40 kilometers from the Romanian border, at that time-- and Polish army units were retreating, running away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't know they were gonna get captured by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do I what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you knew that they were going-- we thought that they were going to the front lines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But actually, we realized that this was part of the retreat-- they were trying to get-- Romania was-- to get to Romania to escape from both of them, I guess.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, then the Russians came in the next day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first thing that came in was Russian tanks-- T-34s which we never saw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Polish army didn't have tanks like that-- they were huge in those-- for those days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as they were coming in, they were greeted by the population-- not by the Polish population, not by-- I don't think by the Ukrainian population, but the Jews felt that they were being liberated from oppression.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I saw what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, it was mostly government property.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, for instance, there was a cigarette warehouse, and cigarettes were government-controlled in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a monopoly, like a government monopoly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody was looting cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were looting the stores or food that belonged to the Polish army or whatever Polish-- because the army was gone, the Polish police was gone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no authority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for that day, or day and a half, civilians picked up guns, and they're trying to control, to hold crime down.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
